---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Reflections">
  <div class="glass-card" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
    <div style="background: white; padding: 1rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; transform: rotate(-1deg); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
       <img src="/Arze_K/home.jpg" alt="Milestones" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" />
       <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">New Beginnings 🏠</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 2rem;">A Season of Gratitude</h2>
    <p style="line-height: 2; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444;">
      "I am so grateful for the blessings I have been given in this lifetime. Both my children are about to graduate, I'm finally a homeowner [Yay!], and ***** Eye Care has provided me the perfect environment to grow..."
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;">
      <button style="background: var(--navy); color: white; border: none; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer;">❤️ Send Warmth</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
